# 架構重構計畫 - 純邊驅動動作 (Pure Edge-Based Actions)

## 目標
將動作執行邏輯從「讀取節點動作」改為「讀取邊的動作」。

> [!CAUTION]
> **不相容舊地圖**：此變更後，舊地圖的節點動作設定將被忽略。需重新設定連結動作。

### Strict Sequential Navigation
The system must ensure the character visits every node in the path sequence, especially those that initiate an action (like a jump).

#### [MODIFY] [PathPlanningTracker.cs](file:///d:/Full_end/C#\ArtaleAI/Core/PathPlanningTracker.cs)
- **Disable Node Skipping**: In [SelectNextTarget](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Core/PathPlanningTracker.cs#1247-1579), strictly select `_currentPathIndex + 1` if the current node has an action or is an edge start point.
- **Enforce Arrival**: Do not switch target until the character is within a very small tolerance (e.g., 5px) of the current target node if it's an action node.
- **Edge Lookup**: Ensure `_currentNavigationEdge` is updated correctly for every segment.

#### [MODIFY] [MainForm.cs](file:///d:/Full_end/C#\ArtaleAI/UI/MainForm.cs)
- **Action Execution**: Verify that [ProcessPathPlanning](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/UI/MainForm.cs#2700-2739) executes the action *only* when at the node, and handles the "arrival" condition correctly to trigger the next target.

## 變更清單

### 1. PathPlanningTracker.cs
- [ ] 新增 `CurrentNavigationEdge` 屬性
- [ ] [SelectNextTarget()](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Core/PathPlanningTracker.cs#1247-1579) 時查詢並設定當前邊
- [ ] 移除「將邊動作回寫到節點」的邏輯 (lines 729-750)

### 2. MainForm.cs
- [ ] [OnPathTrackingUpdated](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/UI/MainForm.cs#2008-2404) 改讀 `Tracker.CurrentNavigationEdge.InputSequence`
- [ ] 移除讀取 `_currentTarget.Action` 的舊邏輯

### 3. PathNode.cs (選用清理)
- [ ] 考慮移除 [Keys](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Core/PathPlanningTracker.cs#466-491) 和 [Action](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/UI/MainForm.cs#107-124) 屬性 (如果不再使用)

## 執行流程 (新架構)

```
1. SelectNextTarget() 選擇下一個目標節點
2. 查詢 _navGraph.GetEdge(玩家附近節點, 目標節點)
3. 存入 CurrentNavigationEdge
4. MainForm 讀取 CurrentNavigationEdge.InputSequence 執行動作
```

## 動態繩索修復 (Dynamic Rope Recovery)

### Core/PathPlanningTracker.cs
#### [MODIFY] UpdatePathState
- **Fall Detection Hook**: 在檢測到墜落時 (dy > FallThreshold)，不再直接返回。
- **Dynamic Rope Check**: 立即呼叫 [FindNearbyRope](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Core/PathPlanningTracker.cs#263-356) 檢查當前位置是否有可用繩索。
- **Force Switch**: 若找到繩索，強制將 `_currentTarget` 切換為繩索入口點，建立臨時節點，啟動繩索導航模式。

## 核心修正 (Core Fixes) - 嚴格順序模式 (Strict Sequential Mode)

### 1. Disable Smart Logic (禁用智慧邏輯)
- **Target Generation**: 在 [SelectNextTarget](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Core/PathPlanningTracker.cs#1247-1579) 中移除/註解掉 [FindNearbyRope](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Core/PathPlanningTracker.cs#263-356) 與 `_ropeNavigator.FindNextRope`。系統不再自動插入繩索節點。
- **Proximity Trigger**: 在 [UpdatePathState](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Core/PathPlanningTracker.cs#932-1044) 中移除/註解掉 [CheckNearbyActionNodes](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Core/PathPlanningTracker.cs#1045-1134)。系統不再允許跳過節點。

### 2. Strict Sequential Execution (嚴格順序執行)
- 確保 [SelectNextTarget](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Core/PathPlanningTracker.cs#1247-1579) 總是簡單地選擇 `_currentPathIndex + 1`。
- 只有當 `Distance < Threshold` 且 [Action](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/UI/MainForm.cs#107-124) 完成時才切換到下一個點。
